  "texts": [
    "The GPT model provides a response that includes the name of the category to which the image belongs.Caption-to-instruction.",
    "Firstly, for image caption datasets, the existing datasets including Syndney-Captions [56], RSICD [37], NWPU-Captions [12], RSITMD [57], and UCM-Captions [56] are cleaned, removing duplicate captions for the same image.",
    "Then the instruction \"Please provide a onesentence caption for the provided RS image in detail.\"",
    "is provided and the EarthGPT model is tasked with describing the image.",
    "The number of captions per image determines the number of conversation rounds."
  ],
